Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to introduce you to the next three guests on the menu.
