Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,at 11.30, and we'll resume at, or 12.30, I'm sorry, we'll resume at 11.30, it'll be a lunch break at 12.30, and lunches will be from 12.30 to 2. I ask that you turn off your cell phones, please, because that does interfere with the lecture, and we won't have Nico here today, he's attending his class reunion, 12 people graduated in this class,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and they only have one every 10 years, so, he wanted to attend the class reunion, he didn't know he'd be here the next 10 years to do it, so, and without you, this is my husband, Dr. Hawkins, and I got all dolled up for today, all dolled up, today the lecture is on, I can't remember what it was, serenity, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:08:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it's helped by divine sedation, and so, how many people are new today, oh, my goodness, grace, it's me, all right, so, our style has been to recapitulate the basics for the people who are new,
