Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is the impediment to a group such as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and very few people in our society transcend 499, the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,very few people transcend the identification with mind, which calibrates in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual reality really becomes emergent and dominant at consciousness level 500,
