Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then begins the transformation of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in which things begin to appear quite differently,
