Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At level 600, you transcend the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin to understand and experience things,
