Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but they didn't print it, letters to the editor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I purposely left duh in there,
