Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so much gain on either side, you know what I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the world suffers, we don't need more freedom of speech, folks,
