Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian paradigm of a this causing a that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not putting it down, all the wonders of modern science and medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the great benefits to mankind have arisen out of science,
