Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in our understanding of reality to the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in reality, the way things come about, including creation,
