Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're seeing is emergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing has the potentiality to emerge as that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which then subsequently has the capacity to emerge and transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're witnessing
