Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing is starting from nothing and then ending up as complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is in a process,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if you lead a contemplative lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a contemplative lifestyle in which you're aligned with the field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the content of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this becomes an apparent phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to witness that everything is spontaneously
