Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that evolution then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is the way creation appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what is sequential is the witnessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because you witness it, witness it, witness it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you set it up in a time frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you add causality,
