Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's energized by intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so the whole process is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,speeded up by intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the power of intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wayne Dyer's book,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Power of Intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is a,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole book is addressed to that specific,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,specific aspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,which we link,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can be spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,respectively scientific,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if somebody puts you down for being spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,look I'm just applying the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,pardon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,if I apply the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and what do you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by E equals times C squared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your counter argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and what do you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see Einstein getting emails saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree with E equals MC squared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of emails I get,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,well you may,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that's freedom of speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from which we need protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so each one of us then represents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and this world is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for bringing forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,our potentiality as an actuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this brings up a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,about wanting to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there are many people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with placards and parades,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who want to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have to first understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the purpose of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is the meaning of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,before you decide you want to change it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,this is sort of like a jungle gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,where we acquire gymnastic skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the maximum karmic opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from the highest to the lowest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thrown into juxtaposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the option at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of choosing a this or a that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the leading edge of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which I call the experiencer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is constantly confronted with,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,choosing a this or choosing a that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the way it's built,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because the emergence of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,on this planet then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,began in a very,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,very primitive form,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we like to recontextualize,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because it eliminates the downside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of traditional religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional religion has had a,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,great beneficial impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's downside is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the animal nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes vilified,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because it becomes vilified,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and labeled as sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,man then has to repress it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I don't have any of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and then project it onto the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cruel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not savage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not vicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by making a,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in Freudian terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ego alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,not acceptable,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the downside of our,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,animal nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,gets repressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when it gets repressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it gets projected onto others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,projected against our self,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll talk about the dualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the book we just finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been presenting that at lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because each level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,has attractions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has aversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so we recapitulate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness throughout all of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and there we see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that the emergence of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which is unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,solely possible via divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of life then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in its earliest form,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we calibrated it as protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,at calibration level one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of animal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is you do not have within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for your own survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when you understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up with compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because animal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is created deficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're deficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the second you're born,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,without your mother's milk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you will soon die,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we're created as deficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and needy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so the core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is neediness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it must always get,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy from out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in the primitive form then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this emerged as,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,some way of sampling,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is this edible or not edible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is this compatible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,not compatible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is this friend or foe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so the experience here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,information probe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the advancing edge of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which we eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,identify as I,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and get stuck with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as a self definition,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which puts us in duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but the animal side then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for eons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's law of survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to overcome that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in society,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to get beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the fixation of the solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it gets transformed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,into symbolic form,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it transforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,survival now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is having a lot of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a big car,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,wealthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,having an education,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,having political power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so it gets transformed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,into symbols,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the innate drivingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is still the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,power over others,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody in their right mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who want power over others,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is beyond me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it activates,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people's consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to have power over others,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,within the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,once you realize that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,any offers of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are very unattractive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember it coming to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,having transcended,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just about everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there was nothing left,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of the silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,came a knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a temptation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the great temptations,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all power is yours now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,own it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:22:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and so,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you're not answerable,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,now you realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're beyond personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all power is yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,love,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is a limitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're going to exploit people,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easy to throw them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not capable of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to throw them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hate to be a slumlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be a moral agony,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't afford the rent anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's out old lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're on your own granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,pack your bags and get,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing that everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that's merely the emergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when the conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are appropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:23:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is the empowerment,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that enables the manifestation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to occur,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is held in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to manifest,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher the level,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the more that is so,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,people of the high consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hold the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even for a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or seconds actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it will tend to manifest,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,watch what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.19,0:24:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that they hold in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need the,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need the things,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.19,0:24:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.67,0:24:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what you hold in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.67,0:24:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to manifest,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,huh,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the greater,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.93,0:24:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,why,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.15,0:24:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,says that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,merely observing a phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.15,0:24:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,already changes it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.26,0:24:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't go into,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the power of the level,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:24:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness of the observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.26,0:25:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they were talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.75,0:25:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,probably in the mid 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.84,0:25:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,astute scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.91,0:25:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe around 450,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.91,0:25:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,460,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.91,0:25:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that's astute science,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.91,0:25:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.06,0:25:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when they look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it changes the outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.06,0:25:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen with,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.06,0:25:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if somebody at 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.06,0:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or 550 or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.06,0:25:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.06,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,likely to manifest,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.06,0:25:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.06,0:25:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so for those who haven't,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,been here before,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.09,0:25:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,recapitulate,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.54,0:25:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.65,0:25:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,keep in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.65,0:25:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,these all have to be transcended,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to reach serenity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.19,0:25:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to get up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.19,0:25:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,early in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and work on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.19,0:25:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all day long,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.19,0:25:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you may not have serenity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.25,0:25:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'll have exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.25,0:25:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.26,0:25:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.26,0:25:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely well known,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.26,0:25:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.26,0:26:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.26,0:26:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,noetic sciences,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.26,0:26:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.26,0:26:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,conference on,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.26,0:26:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,maps of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.26,0:26:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.26,0:26:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhinebeck,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.26,0:26:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.20,0:26:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,maps of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.20,0:26:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.20,0:26:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.20,0:26:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,rather important,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,why,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.20,0:26:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.20,0:26:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the open sesame,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to realizing the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of just about everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.20,0:26:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.76,0:26:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.76,0:26:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.76,0:26:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind has never known,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.76,0:26:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.76,0:26:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,never had any capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.79,0:26:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and usually,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.79,0:26:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what is substituted,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.79,0:26:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is persuasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.79,0:26:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,persuasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.79,0:26:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.79,0:26:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.79,0:26:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,along came the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.79,0:26:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and you had,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.79,0:26:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.79,0:26:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,academic proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.93,0:26:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but we had no way,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of discerning truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.93,0:26:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.93,0:26:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.93,0:26:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of the evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.93,0:26:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.93,0:26:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.93,0:26:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a means,
