Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.96,0:26:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.96,0:26:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.96,0:26:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,within the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:26:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.96,0:26:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.96,0:26:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who then,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.96,0:27:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.96,0:27:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so others,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.96,0:27:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,would know about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.96,0:27:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.08,0:27:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
