Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.08,0:27:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.27,0:27:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but to share,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.27,0:27:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with the world,
