Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.27,0:27:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,fallout,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes known,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.27,0:27:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,completely unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.27,0:27:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.27,0:27:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what we discovered,
