Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.10,0:27:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of a different kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.10,0:27:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it was,
