Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.53,1:50:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,intimidation. No brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.09,1:50:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sit down and get brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.48,1:50:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to memorize anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.81,1:50:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to do
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.85,1:50:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,an inculcated training ritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.93,1:50:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which are really, actually
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.57,1:51:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,indoctrinations. Move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.47,1:51:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Islamic
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.60,1:51:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,terrorists are recruited
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.56,1:51:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,by the way, by the repetition
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.57,1:51:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Wahhabism.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.39,1:51:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-binding.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.67,1:51:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No regulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.05,1:51:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete freedom. People can come and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.77,1:51:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you decide to leave, we're not going
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.13,1:51:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to put a snake in your mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.18,1:51:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoids
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.75,1:51:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,glamorization. Truth attracts
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.02,1:51:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by its own
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.56,1:51:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic power.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.25,1:51:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritually advanced person
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.64,1:51:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're really advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.68,1:51:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of intuits it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.65,1:51:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When they hear it, they go, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.23,1:51:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hear what Socrates said, you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.06,1:51:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,God, yeah, that's, you just instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.43,1:51:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,see the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.72,1:51:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.86,1:51:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-materialistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.44,1:51:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoid of theatrics.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.36,1:51:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.75,1:51:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,seduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.07,1:51:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.88,1:52:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual teacher theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.23,1:52:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The theater of the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.22,1:52:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The theater of the guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.97,1:52:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.22,1:52:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,theatrical production.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.89,1:52:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, theatrical production.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.81,1:52:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.19,1:52:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.26,1:52:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's detached. It's self-fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.46,1:52:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-materialistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.97,1:52:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-intentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.72,1:52:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.77,1:52:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Equality. Non-temporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.85,1:52:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.50,1:52:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ineffable.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.31,1:52:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, mystical.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.52,1:52:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest truths have always been
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.11,1:52:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.85,1:52:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consequence of the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.03,1:52:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self, with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.85,1:52:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you remove
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.96,1:52:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the interferences of the
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.71,1:52:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ego positions, the source
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.85,1:52:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's own existence shines forth
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.89,1:52:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.55,1:53:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditionally called the self, with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.72,1:53:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway of
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.81,1:53:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.06,1:53:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.78,1:53:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people, it's relied via
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.90,1:53:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.19,1:53:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.11,1:53:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,. Incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.89,1:53:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ was an incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.50,1:53:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But by that,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.14,1:53:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the radiance emanates
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.42,1:53:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.10,1:53:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Simplistic, it affirms truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.31,1:53:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.17,1:53:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.39,1:53:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,God doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.02,1:53:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,God is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.90,1:53:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.85,1:53:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To do, you'd have to have a dualistic
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.77,1:53:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,doer and a deed.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.63,1:53:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.56,1:53:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What does anything mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.51,1:53:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thing means
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.43,1:53:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.32,1:53:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What it is, is its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.34,1:54:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that cute?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.60,1:54:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.23,1:54:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What it is, is its meaning
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.34,1:54:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.57,1:54:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you say about it is
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.61,1:54:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is an encumbrance
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.57,1:54:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that really beclouds the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.47,1:54:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a chair mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.61,1:54:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.96,1:54:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.60,1:54:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, what happened to our...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.84,1:54:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She took away the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.43,1:54:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth. Truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.96,1:54:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.85,1:54:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these modern gadgets, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.85,1:54:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.92,1:55:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It went away.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.35,1:55:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see what does it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.35,1:55:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of technology, I don't have a computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.35,1:55:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.56,1:55:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I walk around them because they buzz
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.77,1:55:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and make noises and flashlights and this
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.77,1:55:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,rattles me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.90,1:55:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be doing something with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.55,1:55:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.55,1:55:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, we'll talk then.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.40,1:55:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so spiritual integrity then.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.92,1:55:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've listed a hundred teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.92,1:55:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly, after you've finished with all of them,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.92,1:55:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then write me about some guy who wrote a book
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.92,1:55:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about other dimensions and other times
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.43,1:55:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.43,1:55:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.10,1:55:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've run out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.10,1:55:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity teachers,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.10,1:55:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then write me and ask me what they got to write.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.23,1:55:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, we used to answer them,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.23,1:55:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but then we find it's all over the email
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.23,1:55:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you get,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.23,1:55:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, how come you said so and so, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.39,1:55:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't live in that world.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.39,1:56:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, contention is not a happy lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.88,1:56:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Contention is not conducive to peace of mind.
